Text: Hey Kirby…what’s up!? In a pinch. The wife and I are looking for some greenery to celebrate a birthday…what are the odds you have any and could we possibly scoop some tonight?
Yo dude. I don’t have any extra cartridges, but I do have some bud.
If that works, definitely stop by
Actually you around tomorrow by chance?
Yup I’m working from home tomorrow
What time were you thinking?
Hey buddy sorry I meant to get back to you but I ended up finding some and we are all set but thanks for offering and I’ll see you soon
All good dude, enjoy!
Yo, do you still want to go to that Goose concert Friday the 24th? I have another buddy who is going and we’re trying to figure out tickets
Yes I’m in. Had to confirm on the home front, but I’m good to go
Ok word
My other buddy wants to get floor tickets. Apparently they’re around $100 right now
Before taxes/fees
I’m in for whatever. Floor works
Ok nice. Floor is the best anyway
Yo, lmk if you want to carpool tomorrow. I was thinking of leaving Conshy around like 8:20-8:30ish
I’m actually hitching a ride from Melissa out to nicks and she’s heading out that way. Ready for some golf do you know who were playing with?
Nice! Yeah dude looking forward to it
We are partnered with Nick and one of his friends
Liked “We are partnered with Nick and one of his friends”
Actually Melissa said it would save her time going to your place vs Nick so may just take you up on the offer
Yeah dude whatever works
What time you wanna leave your place
I was thinking 8:20-8:30ish so we can stop at Wawa on the way
First tee time is 10, so we will prob get there around 9-9:15
Address?

115 Merion Ave
Conshohocken, pa
Jumping in shower. Front door is open

Early am round
Lederach Golf Club in Harleysville most likely. Looks legit
Yo dude
I actually already have a tee time that morning for a work golf event at Huntingdon Valley
Let me know how it is! That course always pops up on GolfNow but I’ve never played it
All good! Enjoy. It’s like every cousin in law are all playing golf at the same time but none together.
Haha every one
Hahaha no shit really??
And thank you for the invite.
Oh totally
Let’s get a round
Soon
I just got fitted for clubs, so should have a new set in a month or two
Yeah dude definitely
Also found out the way my driver was set up was somehow 5° open at address. Fucking unreal hahah
Hahaha whaaaat
That’s a first
Was it used?
Nah but it has an adjustable head, so when we got back from Myrtle I put it on the “lower loft” selection and apparently that opens the hell out of the face
Makes no sense at all. But they aligned it so it’s closed .25° now
Yea how do you lower the loft and then close it I dunno man I never trust tinkering with those adjustables never have
Hurts swings more than helps across the board I feel
People just adjust their clubs I feel like bad swings just ingrain more
100%. Now that I have it aligned I’m never changing it again
What irons you get
Going to get the Mizuno JPX 923 Forged
4-PW
prob won’t get them for another 6 weeks or so
Excellent choice. I’m a Mizuno iron guy for life
You were the first person I ever heard talking about them. And then it’s all I’ve seen since
They seem legit
Forged to Japanese precision
Damn looking at yours now. They are beautiful
Everyone gets Taylor made. My friend just left Taylor made as a rep bc he said quality control is so bad it made his job brutal all these members he fit were always calling him with club issues
Thanks dude, hopefully I can hit them haha
No shit. Taylor made used to always be great
That’s crazy they fell off like that from a quality perspective
Apparently grew so fast they couldn’t adjust through Covid
Ahh yeah that actually makes some sense
